headline: Northern Trust Universe Data: Strong 2024 Performance for U.S. Institutional Investors, Despite Q4 Market Volatility
summary: CHICAGO, February 07, 2025--The largest plans in the Northern Trust Universe had a median return of -0.8% in the fourth quarter and 9.4% for the full year in 2024.
